{"tid":815693,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】李嘉欣愛駒「驃寶」操練受傷離世","createTime":"2018-09-12T08:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T08:38:20.000Z","uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"306733ba2bb9a69604222c9debffe5adbf88c4c7","tid":815693,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:31:53.000Z","msg":"許晉亨和李嘉欣（Michele）夫婦購自法國的馬匹「驃寶」，今早七時左右於晨課操練期間受傷離世，終年3歲。「驃寶」抵港僅個多月，來港前出賽9場，取得4冠1亞1季，包括今年5月贏出1100米三級賽Prix Texanita，上月中開始投入操練，如今出師未捷便離世，十分可惜。<br />\n<br />\nMichele今日透過助手回覆《蘋果》，對於愛駒受傷離世感到傷心，她說：「聽到呢個消息一定唔開心，但對馬房百份百信心，亦都相信獸醫嘅決定係正確。」問Michele會否再買馬匹？她則表示：「咁呢個熱情唔會減嘅，都希望買到高質數嘅馬匹。」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Michele和老公許晉亨的養馬運很不錯，贏馬數目亦達十場，最叻是夫婦首匹聯名擁有的愛駒「一寶」，曾多次角逐級際賽，贏走二級賽馬會短途錦標（1200米）、二級賽短途錦標（1200米）及三級賽沙田銀瓶（1400米），最後評分高達108分，取得5冠6亞9季，總獎金超過1,500萬。"},{"pid":"ddede35e590f46adfb032d26d5b211d3487c89d6","tid":815693,"uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif&h=74a0e790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/135859_8ef13172083af6d92739df9095300d9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F135859_8ef13172083af6d92739df9095300d9b.jpg&h=02ebf494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/135910_de6dd01ad3a6bdafd0dfa526dfeb4aad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F135910_de6dd01ad3a6bdafd0dfa526dfeb4aad.jpg&h=f9ef9f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/135928_37617ac1ba4da3954b4e0c85dbd4ade7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F135928_37617ac1ba4da3954b4e0c85dbd4ade7.jpg&h=4b39ffe5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dea1a4875a924e7e2dceb5d1cd26cb8d70684566","tid":815693,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"高質數嘅馬匹<br />\n<br />\n乜李嘉欣D中文咁屎"},{"pid":"0bbf315a0b4c7eb4c11f0091854678553f04ea10","tid":815693,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/163628_0f727354a55e300bca800653da9925d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F163628_0f727354a55e300bca800653da9925d9.png&h=943db39f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 許晉亨和李嘉欣近年相當活躍馬圈，現時名下現役馬除驃寶外，還有陸寶及七寶</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/163648_6d559b1195f89732ad3b4591df469208.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F163648_6d559b1195f89732ad3b4591df469208.png&h=84a7a7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 許晉亨、大摩及韋達（右起）</span>"}]}